176
00:11:58,708 --> 00:12:03,375
I'm not... a normal human being.

177
00:12:03,458 --> 00:12:07,083
I was built for war. I'm no
more than a living weapon.

178
00:12:07,166 --> 00:12:10,166
Believe me, I didn't
ask to be this way...

179
00:12:10,250 --> 00:12:11,458
But I am...

180
00:12:11,541 --> 00:12:13,416
And if I can do something
with these abilities

181
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:16,541
