Do you really think you've won?

252
00:18:44,125 --> 00:18:47,375
If you take my life,
it will accomplish nothing...

253
00:18:47,458 --> 00:18:50,250
I am merely a part
of the program.

254
00:18:50,333 --> 00:18:53,208
When damaged, the program
will repair itself

255
00:18:53,291 --> 00:18:57,750
and return to normal...
And the cycle will continue.

256
00:18:57,833 --> 00:19:00,041
We will feed the
sheep of this nation.

257
00:19:00,125 --> 00:19:03,291
We will shear and slaughter
them as we see fit...

258
00:19:03,375 --> 00:19:04,666
And they will live their lives

259
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:07,416
completely oblivious
to this fact.

260
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:09,333
You and your cause
will be crushed...

261
00:19:09,416 --> 00:19:11,250
Your deaths will be pointless...

262
00:19:11,333 --> 00:19:14,375
You can't possibly
hope to change a thing.

263
00:19:33,666 --> 00:19:36,041
Sei!

264
00:19:36,125 --> 00:19:37,833
Jo.

265
00:19:37,916 --> 00:19:39,750
Shoot that thing!

266
00:19:42,541 --> 00:19:44,625
You just entered
a whole new world...

267
00:19:44,708 --> 00:19:46,500
Welcome to Hell!

268
00:20:54,541 --> 00:20:57,708
Jo... Keep fighting.

269
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:04,666
Farewell. Jo.

270
00:22:29,458 --> 00:22:33,250
I don't know why I can't move

271
00:22:33,333 --> 00:22:37,125
My mind is lost in this cloud

272
00:22:37,208 --> 00:22:44,500
No one even hears my voice
and my tears fall to the ground

273
00:22:44,583 --> 00:22:52,333
It's like my feelings of
loneliness are falling too

274
00:22:52,416 --> 00:22:57,791
The truth is that we
all just want to smile

275
00:22:57,875 --> 00:23:01,750
and smile with each other

276
00:23:01,833 --> 00:23:04,916
It hurts inside
when we don't...

277
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:08,500
we don't... we don't
know what to say

278
00:23:08,583 --> 00:23:13,250
I only hope that
someone will be there,

279
00:23:13,333 --> 00:23:17,333
and be watching over me

280
00:23:17,416 --> 00:23:19,333
so take my hand,

281
00:23:19,416 --> 00:23:28,125
we'll walk tonight
underneath the sky

